   3.8103132335537186`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"42a11c2a-7ce9-424b-8db9-\
ae33990bf763"],

Cell["\<\
The hydrogen atom is the model system that serves as the reference point for \
all of our conceptual pictures of atomic structure. Compared to other atoms, \
it\[CloseCurlyQuote]s a simple system that we can solve exactly, and \
comprehension of the fundamental concepts will provide significant utility in \
analyzing more complex systems.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8103145440169287`*^9, 3.810314674813118*^9}, {
  3.810316197980316*^9, 3.8103161997416105`*^9}, {3.810316258469636*^9, 
  3.810316285452407*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"384599c9-057e-446b-8b89-\
641dd327bfc0"],

