 "Reposition of the ",
 StyleBox["R",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "(",
 StyleBox["r",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ") factor before partial derivatives with respect to \[Phi] or \[Theta] gives"
}], "Text",
