Cell["\<\
Although we looked at the energy constraints for the rigid rotor previously, \
we have yet to solve for the general solution of the angular equation (25). \
Our next step is first perform another round of separation of variables and \
attempt to separate the \[Theta] and \[Phi] components. To that end, we now \
write\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810482452733065*^9, 3.8104824962823257`*^9}, {
  3.810482764436165*^9, 3.8104828270528817`*^9}, {3.8107292288897657`*^9, 
