   3.9170222062299576`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "7e9ef866-4fff-4bb1-a214-c02425e754bb"],
 " can be a positive or negative integer allows us to combine equations (35) \
and (36). "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8106456565918818`*^9, 3.81064567902076*^9}, 
   3.810645720619608*^9, 
