Cell["\<\
Recall from the lesson on the rigid rotor that the quantum-mechanical \
operator for the square of the angular momentum in spherical coordinates is \
given by\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.810660804802985*^9, 3.8106608298111486`*^9}, 
   3.8107125444468503`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"4885269a-36ad-461a-8a86-\
