    3.810725881486649*^9}, 3.8107261709801435`*^9, {3.810982157989756*^9, 
    3.810982199946968*^9}, {3.8109846907233605`*^9, 3.810984732610059*^9}},
  ExpressionUUID->"8633ab7d-a142-48b7-9112-1cb8254645cd"],
 "are degenerate, meaning they have the same energy eigenvalue (remember that \
the energy only depends on ",
 StyleBox["n",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "), a linear combination of these two functions will also have the same \
energy eigenvalue. This is a general property of degenerate eigenfunctions,"
}], "Text",
