   3.8110034996435204`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"f683e882-2c20-4a50-ac6b-\
13788370043a"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "These orbitals can again be visualized in Figure 6.4. With the exception of \
the unique ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  StyleBox[
   SubscriptBox["d", 
    SuperscriptBox["z", 
     StyleBox["2",
      FontSlant->"Plain"]]],
   FontSlant->"Italic"]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.810112811439228*^9, 3.8101128248442793`*^9}, {
    3.810479494926491*^9, 3.8104795038498344`*^9}, {3.810479572543576*^9, 
    3.8104796147383184`*^9}, {3.8104802055659895`*^9, 
    3.8104802433915305`*^9}, {3.8104802785189395`*^9, 
    3.8104802814214115`*^9}, {3.810480477782269*^9, 3.8104805471507206`*^9}, {
    3.8104805927965565`*^9, 3.810480633017248*^9}, {3.8104807595294323`*^9, 
    3.8104809538100047`*^9}, {3.8104811300285854`*^9, 
    3.8104811403007636`*^9}, {3.8104812580010843`*^9, 
    3.8104813317580833`*^9}, {3.81048146789211*^9, 3.8104815557630205`*^9}, {
    3.8104817202872114`*^9, 3.8104817438715935`*^9}, 3.810481790764664*^9, 
    3.810481836241686*^9, {3.810481926951917*^9, 3.810481935802024*^9}, {
    3.8106609069078913`*^9, 3.81066090872985*^9}, {3.8106610360496655`*^9, 
    3.8106610794321012`*^9}, {3.8106611250786457`*^9, 
    3.8106611896874313`*^9}, {3.810718226403468*^9, 3.8107182918531866`*^9}, {
    3.8107241335231433`*^9, 3.81072417963937*^9}, {3.810725731557666*^9, 
    3.810725762073639*^9}, 3.810725827742792*^9, {3.810725864748572*^9, 
    3.810725881486649*^9}, 3.8107261709801435`*^9, {3.810982157989756*^9, 
    3.810982199946968*^9}, {3.81098563222202*^9, 3.810985692262789*^9}, {
    3.810989467587449*^9, 3.810989572572736*^9}},ExpressionUUID->
  "95737d59-b930-48e7-a462-85b124f1a7c9"],
 " atomic orbital, all of the other atomic orbitals differ only with respect \
to the axis of orientation. The reason for using such definitions of linear \
combinations of spherical harmonics, in addition to the simpler real \
representation, is that orientation with respect to an axis in this way can \
facilitate chemical intuition when looking at reactivity of atoms or \
molecules. One can also write out the wavefunctions by replacing the \
spherical harmonics with the corresponding atomic orbital definitions, \
thereby generating a real function to represent the wavefunction rather than \
a complex one."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8109898114746513`*^9, 3.810989869142963*^9}, {
  3.810990079166387*^9, 3.8109901417578425`*^9}, {3.810990457872509*^9, 
  3.8109904989123898`*^9}, {3.917100836152206*^9, 
  3.917100836989267*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7b98361d-f8d3-491c-8c85-\
4eb022ec9c5e"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
A Three-Dimensional Visualization of Electron Probability Density\
\>", "Subsubsection",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8107192356180935`*^9, 3.8107192389984384`*^9}, {
  3.810720092755737*^9, 3.81072009754844*^9}, {3.8107211801768475`*^9, 
  3.810721196999052*^9}, {3.810723622437487*^9, 3.8107236405152397`*^9}, {
  3.8107254010986814`*^9, 3.8107254249521646`*^9}, {3.8109859321201744`*^9, 
  3.8109859565496674`*^9}, {3.8109961726426*^9, 3.810996176848007*^9}, {
  3.810996540118507*^9, 
  3.8109965471684675`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"431ff53d-5512-477d-8cb6-\
ef805674bb0b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "As mentioned above, the graphs of the atomic orbital functions in Figure \
6.4 give a general idea of the shapes of various atomic orbitals, but they do \
not reflect the probability of finding an electron at a given value of (",
 StyleBox["r",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 ", \[Theta], \[Phi]). That information is given by the electron probability \
density function,"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8109965614178095`*^9, 3.8109966867469788`*^9}, {
  3.810996841290862*^9, 3.8109968423022976`*^9}, {3.917100791063648*^9, 
  3.917100791956212*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"014c89e6-f8ee-4a1a-81f7-\
93c3082efe4c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  SubsuperscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["nlm",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["l",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]], "\[Star]"], 
  RowBox[{"(", 
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["r",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], ",", "\[Theta]", ",", "\[Phi]"}], ")"}], 
  SubscriptBox["\[Psi]", 
   SubscriptBox[
    StyleBox["nlm",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], 
    StyleBox["l",
     FontSlant->"Italic"]]], 
  RowBox[{"(", 
   RowBox[{
    StyleBox["r",
     FontSlant->"Italic"], ",", "\[Theta]", ",", "\[Phi]"}], ")"}], 
  SuperscriptBox[
   StyleBox["r",
    FontSlant->"Italic"], "2"], "sin\[Theta]"}]], "DisplayFormulaNumbered",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.810996776714179*^9, {3.9171007699297547`*^9, 
   3.917100776475114*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"66306fd3-6111-4c35-9e60-\
462667319245"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "This function is plotted in Figure 6.5 using a \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]heat \
map\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote], where the color at a given point tells the \
probability of finding an electron at that point. For the ",
 StyleBox["s",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " orbitals, there is not much difference between this plot and the radial \
distribution functions in Figure 6.3 due to the spherical symmetry of the \
radial dependence. For the ",
 StyleBox["p",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " and ",
 StyleBox["d",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " orbitals, however, you can now visualize how the shapes in Figure 6.4 can \
be insufficient to depict to the full complexity of the electron probability \
density."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8109968080394564`*^9, 3.8109969561282744`*^9}, {
  3.8109971379279222`*^9, 3.8109971391697893`*^9}, {3.9171007942426634`*^9, 
  3.9171008096361294`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"7e454313-c516-4808-8207-\
5cfbc4addf9b"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"Manipulate", "[", "\n", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{"Module", "[", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"Prange", "=", 
        RowBox[{"{", 
         RowBox[{
          SuperscriptBox["10", 
           RowBox[{"-", "6"}]], ",", " ", "1"}], "}"}]}], ",", " ", "Ao", ",",
        "p"}], "}"}], ",", "\n", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"If", "[", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"n", "<=", "l"}], ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"l", "=", "0"}]}], "]"}], ";", " ", 
      RowBox[{"If", "[", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"l", "<", 
         RowBox[{"Abs", "[", "m", "]"}]}], ",", " ", 
        RowBox[{"m", "=", "0"}]}], "]"}], ";", "\n", 
      RowBox[{"p", "=", 
       RowBox[{"Function", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{"x", ",", "y", ",", "z"}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
         RowBox[{"huelogf", "[", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"Abs", "[", 
            RowBox[{"Re", "[", " ", 
             RowBox[{"P", "[", 
              RowBox[{
               SqrtBox[
                RowBox[{
                 SuperscriptBox["x", "2"], "+", 
                 SuperscriptBox["y", "2"], "+", 
                 SuperscriptBox["z", "2"]}]], ",", 
               RowBox[{"ArcTan", "[", 
                RowBox[{"z", ",", 
                 SqrtBox[
                  RowBox[{
                   SuperscriptBox["x", "2"], "+", 
                   SuperscriptBox["y", "2"]}]]}], "]"}], ",", 
               RowBox[{"ArcTan", "[", 
                RowBox[{"x", ",", "y"}], "]"}]}], "]"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", 
           " ", "Prange"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", "\n", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"\[Psi]2", "[", 
        RowBox[{"r_", ",", " ", "\[Theta]_", ",", " ", "\[Phi]_"}], "]"}], ":=",
        " ", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Exp", "[", 
         RowBox[{"-", 
          FractionBox[
           RowBox[{"2", " ", "r"}], "n"]}], "]"}], " ", 
        SuperscriptBox[
         RowBox[{"(", 
          FractionBox[
           RowBox[{"2", " ", "r"}], "n"], ")"}], 
         RowBox[{"2", " ", "l"}]], " ", 
        SuperscriptBox[
         RowBox[{"(", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"LaguerreL", "[", 
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"n", "-", "l", "-", "1"}], ",", 
             RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"2", " ", "l"}], "+", "1"}], ",", " ", 
             FractionBox[
              RowBox[{"2", " ", "r"}], "n"]}], "]"}], " ", 
           RowBox[{"LegendreP", "[", 
            RowBox[{"l", ",", 
             RowBox[{"Abs", "[", "m", "]"}], ",", " ", 
             RowBox[{"Cos", "[", "\[Theta]", "]"}]}], "]"}], " ", 
           RowBox[{"Cos", "[", 
            RowBox[{"m", " ", "\[Phi]"}], "]"}]}], ")"}], "2"]}]}], ";", "\n", 
      RowBox[{"Ao", "=", 
       RowBox[{"1", "/", 
        RowBox[{"NIntegrate", "[", 
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{
           SuperscriptBox["r", "2"], " ", 
           RowBox[{"Sin", "[", "\[Theta]", "]"}], "  ", 
           RowBox[{"\[Psi]2", "[", 
            RowBox[{"r", ",", " ", "\[Theta]", ",", " ", "\[Phi]"}], "]"}]}], 
          ",", " ", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"r", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "Infinity"}], "}"}], ",", 
          " ", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"\[Theta]", ",", " ", "0", ",", "\[Pi]"}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"\[Phi]", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", 
            RowBox[{"2", " ", "\[Pi]"}]}], "}"}]}], "]"}]}]}], ";", "\n", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"P", "[", 
        RowBox[{"r_", ",", " ", "\[Theta]_", ",", " ", "\[Phi]_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
       RowBox[{"Ao", " ", 
        RowBox[{"\[Psi]2", "[", 
         RowBox[{"r", ",", " ", "\[Theta]", ",", " ", "\[Phi]"}], "]"}]}]}], 
      ";", "\n", 
      RowBox[{"Pane", "[", 
       RowBox[{"Row", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{"Show", "[", 
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"ParametricPlot3D", "[", 
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"{", 
                RowBox[{
                 RowBox[{"r", " ", 
                  RowBox[{"Sin", "[", "\[Theta]", "]"}]}], ",", " ", "0", ",",
                  " ", 
                 RowBox[{"r", " ", 
                  RowBox[{"Cos", "[", "\[Theta]", "]"}]}]}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
               RowBox[{"{", 
                RowBox[{"r", ",", " ", "0", ",", " ", "15"}], "}"}], ",", " ", 
               RowBox[{"{", 
                RowBox[{"\[Theta]", ",", 
                 RowBox[{"-", 
                  FractionBox["\[Pi]", "2"]}], ",", " ", "\[Pi]"}], "}"}], 
               ",", " ", 
               RowBox[{"ColorFunctionScaling", "->", " ", "False"}], ",", " ", 
               RowBox[{"Mesh", "->", " ", 
                RowBox[{"{", 
                 RowBox[{"50", ",", " ", "50"}], "}"}]}], ",", "  ", 
               RowBox[{"MeshStyle", "->", "None"}], ",", 
               RowBox[{"ColorFunction", "->", " ", "p"}]}], "]"}], ",", " ", 
             "\n", 
             RowBox[{"ParametricPlot3D", "[", 
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"{", 
                RowBox[{
                 RowBox[{"15", " ", 
                  RowBox[{"Cos", "[", "\[Phi]", "]"}], " ", 
                  RowBox[{"Sin", "[", "\[Theta]", "]"}]}], ",", " ", 
                 RowBox[{"15", " ", 
